> My bumper didn't have any really big dents, but a lot of little "Parking
Lot
> Dents", which the guy at Bumper Boyz told me can be more time consuming to
> straighten.

If you have the time and patience, with a good body hammer, body dolly and
file, you can take these parking lot dents out yourself. Takes a little
practice to get the "touch", but the old VW bumper metal is quite workable.

